graphy-reference internal-reference\" href=\"/topics/varicocele/references/\">Crawford et al, 2014</a>] and <em>Adolescent varicocele</em> [<a class=\"bibliography-reference internal-reference\" href=\"/topics/varicocele/references/\">Kass, 2001</a>].</p><!-- end field eb6c8f8a-b9f9-41fc-89ff-a7470091cc08 --><!-- end item 0bd97b69-2790-4e4b-92bb-a7470091cd37 -->","subChapters":[]}]}}},"staticQueryHashes":["3666801979"]}